Package: aibio.r
Type: Package
Title: R Helpers for AI-Bio-T-Cell Project
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sojung", "Kim", email = "sojung.kim.nca@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: R-side utilities for the AI-Bio-T-Cell project. Provides
    helpers for Seurat/Signac preprocessing of RIKEN ReapTEC and related
    T-cell single-cell datasets, enhancer-GWAS overlap analysis with
    GenomicRanges, and visualization helpers for cell state trajectories.
